    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family containing 50 genera and 268 species of small rodents; the term "squirrel" is derived from the Greek "skiouros," meaning "shade tail," which describes one of the animals' most conspicuous and recognizable features.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
